bzh.plealog.hge.api.hypergraph

Interface HDataGraph


  • public interface HDataGraph
    Defines a data hyper-graph describes by a DataGraphModel. The entry point of this interface is the create method: it is used to instantiate a concrete graph given a data model and a data source.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
